===Wins===

* [[Bermuda Bowl]] (2) 1983, 2001 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[Senior Bowl (bridge)|d'Orsi Senior Bowl]] (2) 2005, 2007 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[World Transnational Open Teams Championship]] (1) 2000 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/transnational-open-teams.aspx World Transational Open Teams Winners]</ref>

* [[Rosenblum Cup]] (1) 2006 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-open-teams.aspx Rosenblum Cup Winners]</ref>

* [[Cavendish Invitational|Cavendish Invitational Pairs]] (2) 1976, 1977 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[Buffett Cup]] (2) 2010, 2012 

